snippet.title: Checkered Flag (Atari Jaguar 1994)
snippet.description:
Eventually, I review one game of Atari Jaguar.
First game I review is a primitive polygon 3D racing game.

Firstly, It was released in Atari Lynx (8 bit handheld game console).
Individually, It's not amusing to me, but It is a famous game in Atari Jaguar games.



various information : https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Checkered_Flag_(video_game)
